# Nova Project Conventions

## Monorepo Structure

This is a **pnpm workspace monorepo**. Always use `pnpm` (not npm/yarn).

- `packages/db/` — shared `@aura/db` package (Drizzle schema, migrations, config)
- `apps/api/` — Hono API on Vercel (Slack bot, cron jobs, AI tools)
- `apps/dashboard/` — Next.js admin dashboard
- `apps/web/` — marketing site / blog
- `content/` — blog posts and Mintlify docs

**Import schema via `@aura/db/schema`** in both apps. Never copy schema files.

